OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FShoplifter 'beat the       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsystem' with refund trick  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A 53-year old woman who made half a    
OL,6, million pounds by shoplifting on "an   
OL,7, industrial scale" has been warned to   
OL,8, expect a "substantial" jail sentence.  
OL,10,FNarinder Kaur, 53, tricked high street 
OL,11,Fstores into giving her refunds for     
OL,12,Fgoods she had stolen.                  
OL,14,FShe was found guilty at Gloucester     
OL,15,FCrown Court of 25 separate offences on 
OL,16,FFriday after a four-month trial.       
OL,18,FThe trial heard that it was believed   
OL,19,FKaur had stolen from more than 1,000   
OL,20,Fshops across the country.              
